{"tid":2447700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：若疫情繼續反覆　接種率不理想或「無可避免」再收緊社交限制或關閉處所","createTime":"2021-03-15T11:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T13:23:36.000Z","uid":350584,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b901406209950ea79a035c16540a75cee1862246","tid":2447700,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"政府宣布擴大新冠疫苗接種優先群組範圍，將涵蓋30至59歲人士、在香港以外就讀的16歲或以上學生及家庭傭工，明早9時起可預約接種。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府說，若疫情繼續反覆，確診宗數維持高雙位數，加上新冠疫苗接種率不理想，政府「無可避免」考慮可能再次收緊社交距離措施或關閉處所。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580711-20210315.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580711-20210315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=qonCz35ufBxMHQAS3tFcDm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=5bc5f006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580711-20210315.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d3d3309c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580711-20210315.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"cab5c8d7676860a072e0ebde88bac33d61333139","tid":2447700,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:23:45.000Z","msg":"另外，政府說，若疫情繼續反覆，確診宗數維持高雙位數，加上新冠疫苗接種率不理想，政府「無可避免」考慮可能再次收緊社交距離措施或關閉處所。"},{"pid":"43ef261d8fed31951b6c6d9f2ef150805b1a781b","tid":2447700,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:24:34.000Z","msg":"政府宣布擴大新冠疫苗接種優先群組範圍，將涵蓋30至59歲人士、在香港以外就讀的16歲或以上學生及家庭傭工，明早9時起可預約接種。"},{"pid":"7351f07ee7d414ab74b435e33076915ea97ad598","tid":2447700,"uid":47356,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"繼續收緊你條老到發霉發黑既臭陰道囉"},{"pid":"e8916d3af8458c2295ebf59b0299adc881eaf2ff","tid":2447700,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7351f07ee7d414ab74b435e33076915ea97ad598","tid":2447700,"uid":47356,"like":19,"dislike":0,"